Title: A Return to Krasarang
Description:
Wherever your loyalties might lie - with Rommath and I, with Garrosh, or elsewhere - one thing is true: your acts today were truly heroic.

I can arrange for your transport back to Krasarang Wilds. Speak with me if you would like passage back to Pandaria, $n.
ObjectivesText: Report to General Nazgrim at Domination Point in Krasarang Wilds.
